00:44:25,520 --> 00:44:27,841
Doesn't make a damn bit of difference.

477
00:44:34,280 --> 00:44:37,602
Colonel Carrillo's funeral
will be tomorrow.

478
00:44:39,480 --> 00:44:41,482
[door closes]

479
00:44:41,560 --> 00:44:43,608
I don't do funerals.

480
00:44:45,760 --> 00:44:49,651
[slow Latin guitar music plays]

481
00:46:06,520 --> 00:46:09,330
[in Spanish] They're saying
that Pablo himself killed Carrillo.

482
00:46:09,400 --> 00:46:11,368
Next, he'll come after the two of you.

483
00:46:13,320 --> 00:46:17,006
Or me, or you, Pacho.

484
00:46:17,080 --> 00:46:20,084
N0, no.
