00:46:20,160 --> 00:46:23,448
Another approach.
Another way to achieve our goals.

486
00:46:25,240 --> 00:46:28,722
Pacho, we need to call the Castafios.

487
00:46:30,480 --> 00:46:33,643
Soon we'll know what's in it for them.

488
00:46:40,680 --> 00:46:44,685
- [rain pattering]
- [approaching footsteps]

489
00:46:46,560 --> 00:46:49,769
[thunder rumbles]

