and they're already asking for my head.

491
00:47:12,760 --> 00:47:14,808
They want a scapegoat.

492
00:47:16,600 --> 00:47:18,284
And we have to give them one.

493
00:47:23,400 --> 00:47:24,686
[sighs]

494
00:47:27,720 --> 00:47:31,441
