and without authorization

497
00:47:42,000 --> 00:47:44,048
when I entered La Catedral.

498
00:47:44,760 --> 00:47:48,924
And that it was I who insisted
that Carrillo return.

499
00:47:56,240 --> 00:47:57,880
[Gaviria]
I don't accept your resignation.

500
00:47:57,920 --> 00:48:02,448
