the press, the opposition, the citizens,

503
00:48:11,840 --> 00:48:14,810
everyone's looking for someone to blame.
All of them.

504
00:48:15,760 --> 00:48:17,444
And it's not going to be you.

505
00:48:23,320 --> 00:48:29,123
It's been my honor serving you
and the people of Colombia.

506
00:48:46,120 --> 00:48:47,531
[softly] Good luck.

507
00:48:59,120 --> 00:49:02,283
[bell tolling]

508
00:49:59,880 --> 00:50:02,645
Limén told me you have a daughter.

509
00:50:05,400 --> 00:50:06,606
How old?

510
00:50:10,280 --> 00:50:13,329
- Two.
- And what's her name?

511
00:50:16,040 --> 00:50:19,169
- Salome.
- What a beautiful name.

512
00:50:26,800 --> 00:50:30,521
This is the second time
that I've felt indebted to you.

513
00:50:34,960 --> 00:50:40,330
Now, Maritza...
our daughters will be safe.

514
00:50:42,280 --> 00:50:43,611
Thank you.

515
00:50:45,600 --> 00:50:50,447
Know that... you have a friend in me.

516
00:51:06,880 --> 00:51:07,880
What did you do?

517
00:51:09,960 --> 00:51:11,485
I took care of it.

518
00:51:12,840 --> 00:51:14,490
You're safe now.

519
00:51:15,080 --> 00:51:16,525
[La Quica] Limén.

520
00:52:13,320 --> 00:52:14,810
(H9)'-

