00:52:17,080 --> 00:52:18,764
What are you doing here?

522
00:52:23,720 --> 00:52:25,131
Where's Olivia?

523
00:52:25,200 --> 00:52:28,170
She's at home. With my sister.

524
00:52:38,920 --> 00:52:40,410
Hey, you okay?

525
00:52:48,400 --> 00:52:50,402
- [whimpers]
- Hey.

526
00:52:57,000 --> 00:52:58,570
[soft sobs]

527
00:53:18,480 --> 00:53:20,005
[in Spanish]
What now?

528
00:53:20,720 --> 00:53:22,449
What the fuck do you want?

529
00:53:23,240 --> 00:53:25,004
I want to help you.

530
